title="Alex Nelson">Alex Nelson</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {F}\subseteq \Bbbk \subseteq \mathbb {L}]]></fr:tex> be fields. Suppose <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\Bbbk  / \mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex> is an <fr:link
type="local"
href="nt-000T.xml"
addr="nt-000T"
title="Algebraic Element">algebraic extension</fr:link>. If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\alpha \in \mathbb {L}]]></fr:tex> is algebraic over <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\Bbbk ]]></fr:tex>, then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\alpha ]]></fr:tex> is algebraic over <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
